---

## PostgreSQL Management

```powershell
# Start PostgreSQL
$pgDir = "C:\laragon\bin\postgresql\pgsql"
$env:Path = "$pgDir\bin;$env:Path"
& "$pgDir\bin\pg_ctl.exe" -D "C:\laragon\bin\postgresql\data" -l "C:\laragon\bin\postgresql\data\pg.log" start

# Stop PostgreSQL
& "$pgDir\bin\pg_ctl.exe" -D "C:\laragon\bin\postgresql\data" stop

# Check status
& "$pgDir\bin\pg_isready.exe"

# Connect to psql
psql -U postgres -d mimatcha_db
```

---

## Perubahan MySQL → PostgreSQL (Ringkasan)

| MySQL | PostgreSQL |
|---|---|
| `AUTO_INCREMENT` | `GENERATED ALWAYS AS IDENTITY` |
| `TINYINT(1)` | `SMALLINT` |
| `LONGTEXT` | `TEXT` |
| `ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP` | Trigger `BEFORE UPDATE` |
| `new mysqli(...)` | `new PDO("pgsql:...")` |
| `$stmt->bind_param(...)` | `$stmt->execute([...])` |
| `$conn->insert_id` | `$conn->lastInsertId()` |
| `ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE` | `ON CONFLICT ... DO UPDATE SET` |
| `CURDATE()` | `CURRENT_DATE` |
| `DATE_ADD(CURDATE(), INTERVAL n DAY)` | `CURRENT_DATE + INTERVAL '1 day' * n` |
| `YEAR(col)` | `EXTRACT(YEAR FROM col)` |

